org.tensorics.core.booleans.operations

Class LogicalTensorOperationsRepository

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.tensorics.core.booleans.operations.LogicalTensorOperationsRepository

  • public final class LogicalTensorOperationsRepository
extends java.lang.Object
    Reposirtory for the logical operations for Tensor<>:
  • AND and()
  • AND and(OptionRegistry)
  • AND nand()
  • AND nand(OptionRegistry)
  • OR or()
  • OR or(OptionRegistry)
  • XOR xor()
  • XOR xor(OptionRegistry)

    • For OptionRegistry that supports the operations.

  • defaultRegistry() returns default options registry that contains the following Options: ExactShapesOrOneZeroStrategy, LeftContextPreservedStrategy, BroadcastMissingDimensionsStrategy
  • defaultRegistry(List) returns the defaultRegistry() with overriden options form the provided list
